data.description: Beautifully upgraded multi-level condo in the heart of Boulder. Quiet neighborhood located mere minutes from all of your favorite Boulder activities. New recessed lighting throughout the home, new dining room light fixture, new countertops, new kitchen sink, freshly painted, updated flooring throughout the home, updated bathroom, and newer kitchen appliances. We look forward to welcoming you into your new home!
